flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Librarian opens Category Management]
    B --> C{Authorized Librarian?}
    C -->|No| C1[Access denied] --> Z([End])
    C -->|Yes| D[Show category table]
    D --> E{Action?}
    E -->|Add| F[Enter category name]
    F --> G{Name valid and <= 50?}
    G -->|No| G1[Show validation error] --> F
    G -->|Yes| H[Create category] --> D
    E -->|Edit inline| I[Update name]
    I --> J{Name valid and <= 50?}
    J -->|No| J1[Show validation error] --> I
    J -->|Yes| K[Save category] --> D
    E -->|Delete| L{Any books in category?}
    L -->|Yes| L1[Block delete and show reason] --> D
    L -->|No| M[Confirm delete]
    M --> N{Confirmed?}
    N -->|No| D
    N -->|Yes| O[Delete category] --> D
    E -->|Exit| Z
    Z([End])
